<p>Suburban areas like Westlake and Lakewood typically offer excellent solar potential with unobstructed roof access and newer electrical systems compatible with solar installations. These neighborhoods also commonly require HVAC system upgrades as homes age, creating opportunities for comprehensive energy efficiency improvements combining solar and high-efficiency heating and cooling systems.</p>

